I have been granted the opportunity to bring @adidasoriginals back home to Jamaica. It is an honor to take you all on a journey to where it all began, at my grandmother’s home in Mandeville. This life-changing moment has allowed me to cement my family’s legacy and share this vulnerable yet liberating experience with you all. 

This is dedicated to all women of color and immigrants who have dreamed big. Thank you to my supporters, who have been a guiding light on this journey and championed me along the way. Lastly, thank you to Adidas for allowing me to dream big, even bigger than I could have ever imagined. 🖤
